msgstr "此選項需要 curl 軟體包。啟用前請先在軟體包管理中安裝 curl。"

msgid "map.sh Management"
msgstr "map.sh 管理"

msgid "OpenWrt's map.sh has bugs: only the first port group works and ICMP is broken. Click below to replace with the fixed version."
msgstr "OpenWrt 的 map.sh 存在 bug：僅第一組連接埠可用且 ICMP 無法工作。點擊下方按鈕替換為修復版。"

